{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839876132,"sessionID":"ses_287b43300ffeQeeG6q2U6XucfS","part":{"id":"prt_d784ce123001W1yAlxmHqQ2iF2","messageID":"msg_d784c2021001vJ8oMhysqRu52z","sessionID":"ses_287b43300ffeQeeG6q2U6XucfS","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-70d2ae6a432e4895b63afefb589b2b90","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/spec.md","content":"# AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，包括:\n- `CodeInterpreter` 类型及其 `Spec`、`Status`\n- `CodeInterpreterList` 类型\n- `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` 类型\n- `AuthModeType` 枚举及常量定义\n\n## Out of Scope\n\n- Controller 实现\n- Webhook 验证逻辑\n- CRD YAML 生成\n- client-go 代码生成\n- AgentRuntime CRD（已在 AR-001 中定义）\n\n## Dependencies\n\n依赖 AR-001 中定义的共享类型：\n- `TargetPort`\n- `ProtocolType`\n\n## Deliverables\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` | CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | AuthModeType 等共享类型（如需新增） |\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] 类型定义符合 Kubernetes API conventions\n- [ ] JSON tags 使用 camelCase\n- [ ] 包含完整的字段注释\n- [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n- [ ] Enum 验证标记正确\n\n## References\n\n- Kubernetes API Conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n- AR-001 Design: `changes/AR-001/design.md`"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/spec.md","time":{"start":1775839876093,"end":1775839876130}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839876134,"sessionID":"ses_287b43300ffeQeeG6q2U6XucfS","part":{"id":"prt_d784cbaef001wsnK5G26zqOYmj","messageID":"msg_d784c2021001vJ8oMhysqRu52z","sessionID":"ses_287b43300ffeQeeG6q2U6XucfS","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-93da692588f34a95b01192417578c202","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/proposal.md","content":"# AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Proposal\n\n## Purpose\n\nDefine the Go type structures for `CodeInterpreter` CRD in the `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` package. This CRD provides a specialized sandbox runtime for code execution environments with enhanced features:\n\n1. **Warm Pool Management**: Pre-provisioned sandboxes for low-latency startup\n2. **Authentication Integration**: Support for picod auth mode\n3. **Port Exposure**: HTTP/HTTPS endpoints for code interpreter communication\n4. **Resource Management**: CPU/Memory limits for code execution sandboxes\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` | Type definitions for CodeInterpreter, CodeInterpreterSpec, CodeInterpreterStatus, CodeInterpreterList |\n| Supporting types | CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate, AuthModeType constants, validation markers |\n\n### Type Definitions Required\n\n#### CodeInterpreter\n\n```\nCodeInterpreter\n├── Spec\n│   ├── Ports ([]TargetPort, JSON: ports)\n│   ├── Template (*CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate, JSON: template, required)\n│   ├── SessionTimeout (*metav1.Duration, default: 15m)\n│   ├── MaxSessionDuration (*metav1.Duration, default: 8h)\n│   ├── WarmPoolSize (*int32)\n│   └── AuthMode (AuthModeType, default: picod, enum: picod|none)\n├── Status\n│   ├── Conditions ([]metav1.Condition)\n│   └── Ready (*bool)\n└── List: CodeInterpreterList\n```\n\n#### Supporting Types\n\n- `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`: Image, command, args, env, resources, runtimeClassName, imagePullPolicy, imagePullSecrets\n- `AuthModeType`: Enum for picod/none authentication modes\n\n### Out of Scope\n\n- Controller implementation (`pkg/controllers/`)\n- Webhook validation logic\n- CRD YAML generation (handled by `make gen-crd`)\n- client-go code generation (handled by `make gen-client`)\n- AgentRuntime CRD (handled in AR-001)\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### Upstream Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Impact |\n|------------|--------|\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery` | Required for metav1.ObjectMeta, metav1.Duration, metav1.Condition |\n| `k8s.io/api/corev1` | Required for PodSpec elements (EnvVar, PullPolicy, ResourceRequirements) |\n\n### Downstream Consumers\n\n| Consumer | Usage |\n|----------|-------|\n| `make gen-crd` | Generates CRD YAML to `manifests/charts/base/crds/` |\n| `make gen-client` | Generates typed clients, informers, listers |\n| Workload Manager | Creates Sandbox/SandboxClaim instances from CodeInterpreter specs |\n| Router | Routes code interpreter requests to appropriate sandboxes |\n\n## Risks\n\n| Risk | Mitigation |\n|------|------------|\n| Warm pool size validation | Consider webhook for min/max values |\n| AuthMode enum changes | Pin enum values in design doc |\n| Status field extensions | Reserve fields for future use |\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n1. **Boilerplate**: Use `hack/boilerplate.go.txt` header\n2. **JSON Tags**: camelCase per project conventions\n3. **Kubebuilder Markers**: Apply validation markers for required fields and enums\n4. **Printer Columns**: Add Age column for `kubectl get` output\n\n## References\n\n- Kubernetes API Conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n- Kubebuilder Book: https://book.kubebuilder.io/"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775839876089,"end":1775839876133}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839876137,"sessionID":"ses_287b43300ffeQeeG6q2U6XucfS","part":{"id":"prt_d784e13cc001WHl0MMIjH2lbpf","messageID":"msg_d784c2021001vJ8oMhysqRu52z","sessionID":"ses_287b43300ffeQeeG6q2U6XucfS","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-26986534d85c48dcb7f1af6f846bd262","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/tasks.md","content":"# AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Design | [Stage ST-0 pending] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Type Definitions\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Create or update `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n  - Define `CodeInterpreter` struct with markers:\n    - `+genclient`\n    - `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\n    - `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n    - `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`\n    - `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`\n    - `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"`\n  - Define `CodeInterpreterSpec` with fields:\n    - `Ports []TargetPort` (optional, JSON: ports)\n    - `Template *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` (required, JSON: template)\n    - `SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration` (default: 15m)\n    - `MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration` (default: 8h)\n    - `WarmPoolSize *int32` (optional)\n    - `AuthMode AuthModeType` (default: picod, enum: picod|none)\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2** Define `CodeInterpreterStatus`\n  - `Conditions []metav1.Condition` (optional)\n  - `Ready bool` (optional)\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n\n- [ ] **T1.3** Define `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`\n  - `Labels map[string]string`\n  - `Annotations map[string]string`\n  - `RuntimeClassName *string`\n  - `Image string`\n  - `ImagePullPolicy corev1.PullPolicy`\n  - `ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference`\n  - `Environment []corev1.EnvVar`\n  - `Command []string`\n  - `Args []string`\n  - `Resources corev1.ResourceRequirements`\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n\n- [ ] **T1.4** Define `CodeInterpreterList`\n  - Add markers: `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n\n### Phase 2: Shared Types\n\n- [ ] **T2.1** Create or update `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n  - Define `AuthModeType string`\n  - Define constants:\n    - `AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"`\n    - `AuthModeNone AuthModeType = \"none\"`\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n\n### Phase 3: Code Generation\n\n- [ ] **T3.1** Run `controller-gen object paths=./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n  - Verify: `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` includes CodeInterpreter types\n  - Verify: All types implement `runtime.Object` interface\n\n- [ ] **T3.2** Run `controller-gen crd paths=./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... output:crd:dir=manifests/charts/base/crds`\n  - Verify: `codeinterpreters` CRD YAML generated\n\n- [ ] **T3.3** Run `client-gen` to generate client-go code\n  - Verify: CodeInterpreter client generated in `client-go/`\n\n### Phase 4: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **T4.1** Create or update `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n  - Test DeepCopy for `CodeInterpreter`\n  - Test default values: `sessionTimeout=15m`, `maxSessionDuration=8h`, `authMode=picod`\n  - Test enum validation for `AuthModeType`\n  - Test JSON serialization/deserialization\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -v`\n\n### Phase 5: Validation & Quality\n\n- [ ] **T5.1** Run `go vet ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n  - Fix any issues reported\n\n- [ ] **T5.2** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n  - Fix any linting issues\n\n- [ ] **T5.3** Verify JSON tags use camelCase\n  - Check: `ports`, `template`, `sessionTimeout`, `maxSessionDuration`, `warmPoolSize`, `authMode`\n  - Check: `imagePullPolicy`, `imagePullSecrets`, `environment`\n\n- [ ] **T5.4** Verify Kubernetes API conventions compliance\n  - Required fields have `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` marker\n  - Optional fields have `+optional` marker\n  - Default values specified with `+kubebuilder:default=...`\n\n### Phase 6: Documentation\n\n- [ ] **T6.1** Add godoc comments to all exported types and fields\n- [ ] **T6.2** Verify package-level documentation describes CodeInterpreter purpose\n\n---\n\n## Task Dependencies\n\n```\nT1.1 → T1.2 → T1.3 → T1.4\n                      ↓\n                    T2.1\n                      ↓\n                    T3.1 → T3.2 → T3.3\n                                     ↓\n                                   T4.1\n                                     ↓\n                      T5.1 → T5.2 → T5.3 → T5.4\n                                     ↓\n                                   T6.1 → T6.2\n```\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n| Task | Verification Command |\n|------|----------------------|\n| T1.1-T1.4, T2.1 | `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` |\n| T3.1 | `grep -q \"CodeInterpreter\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` |\n| T3.2 | `test -f manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml` |\n| T3.3 | `test -d client-go/clientset` |\n| T4.1 | `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -v -cover` |\n| T5.1 | `go vet ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` |\n| T5.2 | `golangci-lint run ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` |\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] CodeInterpreter types defined per design.md specification\n- [ ] JSON tags use camelCase\n- [ ] Complete field comments for all exported types\n- [ ] Pass `go vet` with zero issues\n- [ ] Pass `golangci-lint` with zero issues\n- [ ] DeepCopy methods generated and functional\n- [ ] CRD YAML generated successfully\n- [ ] client-go code generated successfully\n- [ ] Unit tests pass with >80% coverage\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- Follow Kubernetes API conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n- Use controller-tools v0.17.2 for code generation\n- Reference implementation path (if available): `/tmp/agentcube-ref/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n- Coordinate with AR-001 for shared types (`TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`)"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775839876102,"end":1775839876135}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839876141,"sessionID":"ses_287b43300ffeQeeG6q2U6XucfS","part":{"id":"prt_d784d724b0011AK0094rD5fcRO","messageID":"msg_d784c2021001vJ8oMhysqRu52z","sessionID":"ses_287b43300ffeQeeG6q2U6XucfS","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-1d255fbc9bc44bcbaf54d20c814f56e2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/design.md","content":"# AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，用于代码解释器沙箱运行时。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\nCodeInterpreter CRD 类型定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n- 使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema\n- 类型定义与 DeepCopy 代码分离，由 controller-gen 自动生成\n- 支持 status subresource，用于控制器更新资源状态\n- Namespaced scope，每个命名空间内独立管理代码解释器实例\n\n### Dependencies\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| `k8s.io/api/core/v1` | EnvVar、PullPolicy、ResourceRequirements、LocalObjectReference |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1` | TypeMeta、ObjectMeta、Condition、Duration |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema` | GroupVersion、GroupVersionResource |\n\n### Controller-gen Markers\n\n| Marker | Applied to | Purpose |\n|--------|------------|---------|\n| `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` | Main type + List type | 注册到 Scheme |\n| `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` | Main type | 启用 status subresource |\n| `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced` | Main type | 命名空间级别资源 |\n| `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\"` | Main type | kubectl 输出列 |\n| `+genclient` | Main type | 生成 typed client |\n| `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...` | Main type + List type | DeepCopy 接口 |\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### CodeInterpreter Types\n\n```go\n// +genclient\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n// +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n// +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n// +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\ntype CodeInterpreter struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n    Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n    // +optional\n    Ports []TargetPort `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    Template *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate `json:\"template\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n    SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    WarmPoolSize *int32 `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"picod\"\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\n    // +optional\n    AuthMode AuthModeType `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n    // +optional\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    Ready bool `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n    // +optional\n    Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    RuntimeClassName *string `json:\"runtimeClassName,omitempty\"`\n    Image string `json:\"image,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    ImagePullPolicy corev1.PullPolicy `json:\"imagePullPolicy,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    // +patchMergeKey=name\n    // +patchStrategy=merge\n    // +listType=map\n    // +listMapKey=name\n    ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference `json:\"imagePullSecrets,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    Environment []corev1.EnvVar `json:\"environment,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    // +listType=atomic\n    Command []string `json:\"command,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    Args []string `json:\"args,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    Resources corev1.ResourceRequirements `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n}\n\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\ntype CodeInterpreterList struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Items           []CodeInterpreter `json:\"items\"`\n}\n```\n\n### Shared Types\n\n```go\ntype AuthModeType string\n\nconst (\n    AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n    AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n)\n```\n\n## API Schema\n\n### CRD OpenAPI Constraints\n\n| Resource | Required Spec Fields |\n|----------|----------------------|\n| CodeInterpreter | `template` |\n\n### Defaults\n\n| Field | Default Value |\n|-------|---------------|\n| `sessionTimeout` | `15m` |\n| `maxSessionDuration` | `8h` |\n| `authMode` | `picod` |\n| `ports[].protocol` | `HTTP` |\n\n### Enums\n\n| Field | Allowed Values |\n|-------|----------------|\n| `authMode` | `picod`, `none` |\n\n### REST Resource Plural\n\n| Kind | Plural |\n|------|--------|\n| CodeInterpreter | `codeinterpreters` |\n\n### Printer Columns\n\n| Name | Type | JSONPath |\n|------|------|----------|\n| Age | date | `.metadata.creationTimestamp` |\n\n## Error Handling\n\n- 缺少必填字段 `template` 时，API server 拒绝创建请求\n- 无效 enum 值时，API server 返回 validation error\n- Duration 格式错误时，使用 Go `metav1.Duration` 解析失败抛出错误\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n| Test Category | Coverage |\n|---------------|----------|\n| DeepCopy generation | 确保 DeepCopy 方法正确复制所有字段 |\n| Default values | 验证 kubebuilder 默认值标记生效 |\n| Enum validation | 测试 `authMode` 所有允许值及无效值 |\n| JSON serialization | 验证 JSON tag 正确映射 |\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n- CRD 安装验证：确保 `make gen-crd` 生成的 YAML 可被 k8s API server 接受\n- Client-go 生成验证：`make gen-client` 生成的 client/informer/lister 可正常使用\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\npkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n  codeinterpreter_types.go — CodeInterpreter、CodeInterpreterList、CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate\n  shared_types.go           — AuthModeType 常量（如需新增）\n```\n\n## Generation Commands\n\n| Command | Output |\n|---------|--------|\n| `make generate` | DeepCopy 代码 + CRD YAML |\n| `make gen-client` | client-go（clientset、informers、listers） |\n\n## References\n\n- Source: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n- client-go: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n- controller-tools version: `v0.17.2`"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/design.md","time":{"start":1775839876098,"end":1775839876138}}}}
